asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2006, 2007, 2008 and 2009 Chevy Corvette Z06 with the 7.0L engine. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-3060-1

K&N dynamometer tests show a 27.22 horsepower gain with use of this K&N air intake modification.

2009 CHEVROLET CORVETTE Z06 7.0L V8 
2008 CHEVROLET CORVETTE Z06 7.0L V8 
2007 CHEVROLET CORVETTE Z06 7.0L V8 
2006 CHEVROLET CORVETTE Z06 7.0L V8
